    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I'm selling my car and it has been such a joy to drive! It's in really solid shape, runs beautifully, and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It\u2019s perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend road trips. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
