    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) represents a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS, delivering exceptional throttle response and a linear power band to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system refresh. The suspension retains its factory-tuned kinematics, offering precise turn-in and lateral stability. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain integrity and chassis dynamics remain sharp, making it an ideal candidate for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Mechanically sound. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs well.",
