    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity to own a well-cared-for car that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint still holds a beautiful luster, showing only the minor, superficial nicks one would expect from a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. All body panels are straight, and the original alloy wheels are in great shape. Step inside to a cabin that has been kept in impressive condition; the upholstery is free of rips or stains, and it has never been smoked in. Every feature, from the power windows to the cruise control and the crisp audio system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, reflecting a history of regular oil changes and proactive maintenance. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains firm and responsive, providing a comfortable and secure ride. There are no known mechanical leaks or warning lights on the dash. With a recent service just completed and plenty of life left in the tires and brakes, this car is truly turn-key and ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 31500.0,
