      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my awesome car. It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in really solid shape\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable ride that's been well-taken care of. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is ready for some new adventures! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
