      "description": "This 2003 E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of BMW\u2019s high-revving masterpiece. At its heart is the S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS, delivering a 7,900 RPM redline with exceptional throttle response. The power is managed via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock. Significant technical upkeep has been prioritized, including a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a recent VANOS service to ensure timing precision. The chassis maintains its signature balance through refreshed bushings and factory-tuned suspension kinematics. This is a driver-oriented machine, offering the tactile feedback and analog engagement that defines the M-division's golden era.",
